Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.85,0:01:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月月殖民地的存在\n本來就很令人驚訝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.95,0:01:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且光之族好像問題更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.96,0:01:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被綁走了\n被迫與美麗小姐和姬娜在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.04,0:01:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後戈圖還派出MS大隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.44,0:01:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後莫名奇妙的光之族與教祖都奉承我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.93,0:01:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且拉莎拉與莎拉莎,是同一個人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.52,0:01:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十五話\n幻影殖民地 下集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.15,0:02:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什麼?拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.18,0:02:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉?我不是拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.94,0:02:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是莎拉莎.月\n統治光之族的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.29,0:02:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉莎大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著,羅爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.55,0:02:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要與這個少年談話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.41,0:02:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事態糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.77,0:02:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就是教祖啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.09,0:02:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你必須以救世主的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.36,0:02:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫我把光之教傳播到全世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.07,0:02:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.74,0:02:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她不是再說笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.69,0:02:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光之族的教祖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.23,0:02:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想利用你們的力量\n把光之族的宗教傳播到全宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.20,0:02:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個作法一定會破壞\n月月殖民地的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.00,0:02:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少年!把你的生命交給月月吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.78,0:02:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為我離開這裏的嚮導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你振作點,拉莎拉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你被施予催眠術了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快清醒啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.46,0:03:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無禮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.77,0:03:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉!快清醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.38,0:03:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種無理的人\n不可能是救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.10,0:03:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把這些人關進地下牢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.61,0:03:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些人瘋了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.89,0:03:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.88,0:03:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.95,0:03:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.17,0:03:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們省省吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前面的人走開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.96,0:03:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾美莉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.86,0:03:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾美莉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.47,0:03:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.41,0:03:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.83,0:03:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾美莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.00,0:03:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事...全身有點痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.10,0:04:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追,別讓那些小孩跑掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.52,0:04:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾美莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.96,0:04:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.90,0:04:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先回去亞加瑪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.28,0:04:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達在神殿的前面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼那時候不上去呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管矛有多危險\n被射中還是會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.26,0:04:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉那女孩想幹什麼阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.99,0:04:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度你\n看到美麗的女人就頭昏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.59,0:04:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.13,0:04:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你看到我怎麼沒頭昏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.04,0:04:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想跟比查打架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.01,0:04:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟比查又沒有訂婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.05,0:04:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查說過類似的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.27,0:04:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼啊?可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.84,0:04:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.21,0:04:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉的人來了,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.17,0:04:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉?他們用小鋼珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.58,0:04:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請從後面上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後我在解釋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.01,0:05:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速度加快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,莫迪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.47,0:05:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪?\n幹什麼用這種眼光看著我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是去安多拉嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個說來話長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我幫忙救了你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.02,0:05:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,這女孩不是莎拉莎嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.24,0:05:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼?他是拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.12,0:05:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是莎拉莎.月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.17,0:05:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉,這倒底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.53,0:05:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽說你們\n見過姐姐拉莎拉才追過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.80,0:05:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐莎拉莎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.19,0:05:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說你們是雙胞胎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.21,0:05:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐被奉為光之族的教祖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.88,0:05:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就變的自大起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.18,0:05:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她以為\n只要把光之教傳播到全宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.51,0:05:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭就會消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.57,0:05:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是光靠各位的兩艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.34,0:05:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將光之教傳播出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.39,0:05:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們認為打仗的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會相信這教義嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教義?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.86,0:06:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是配合祥和的月光波長\n和平活下去的教義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.93,0:06:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看這個還是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.48,0:06:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,限於月月地方就好了\n為什麼他想離開殖民地呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.26,0:06:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是她嚮往\n殖民地之前的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.69,0:06:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是過度相信力量的錯誤慾望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.85,0:06:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉,你要去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去神殿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊奴娜地下道的入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燈點亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎? 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.72,0:06:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.33,0:06:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用手電筒不是比較方便嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.61,0:06:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?萬一燈熄了\n就表示附近有毒瓦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.63,0:06:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊走,請到神殿下面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.72,0:07:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是要坐這個去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.42,0:07:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個不會動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.93,0:07:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許可以動..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.79,0:07:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了!要打開電源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.13,0:07:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.55,0:07:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會動嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.99,0:07:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是莫迪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.36,0:07:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好你們有人精通機器\n實在太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.35,0:07:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很榮幸幫你的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.83,0:07:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你卻背叛雅加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.84,0:07:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了賺錢還想把高達壓成廢鐵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.37,0:07:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你被人討厭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們本來就是賣廢鐵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.03,0:07:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是會使用機器的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.22,0:07:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正在思考\n搜索秘密地下道的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.02,0:07:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點,相信機器力量的人\n除了破壞之外不會帶來什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.77,0:07:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個凱特爾正說明了\n機器是多麼無力的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.19,0:08:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些愚蠢的人\n連這個都不瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.12,0:08:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安多拉的人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.31,0:08:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,他們很溫馴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.01,0:08:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪之船也交給他們控制吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.99,0:08:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法,只好藉助他們的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種待遇太不人道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.32,0:08:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別輕舉妄動,受傷就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.75,0:08:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那教祖說畫像廢鐵班\n完全不可理喻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老囉唆,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這地方不大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍與矛都很難用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別一直拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.53,0:08:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是ㄚ,你欠我一個人情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.96,0:08:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了,我自己解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.81,0:08:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有辦法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.26,0:08:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫我解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.58,0:08:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保持原狀比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.33,0:09:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位,快到這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.29,0:09:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教祖怎麼會在這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.86,0:09:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,詳情以後再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.07,0:09:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.44,0:09:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了擴張光之教\n你們把船借給我用就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不是跟亞加瑪聯手了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.39,0:09:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們已經拒絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.17,0:09:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉莎.月大人\n成為宇宙的主人之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.22,0:09:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳送一個殖民地給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.35,0:09:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多麼榮幸的條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.30,0:09:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖,可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.29,0:09:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是花費彈藥\n而奪的一個殖民星的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.05,0:09:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越深入瞭解這個殖民地\n我的心越被光之教吸引
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.19,0:09:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到我這樣的小人\n也能成為光之子民啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.53,0:09:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你肯幫忙嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.40,0:09:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了表示我的決心\n我很樂意效勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.58,0:09:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,把那具大機器拆掉\n丟到安多拉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.41,0:09:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.34,0:09:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終點是亞加瑪所在的港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.56,0:10:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.33,0:10:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搶回ZZ高達再回亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.57,0:10:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼又要綁我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是亞加瑪的俘虜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.05,0:10:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還不知道安多拉的動向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜也過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.25,0:10:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到亞加瑪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.43,0:10:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.45,0:10:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.68,0:10:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.47,0:10:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉,對不起\n帶我去ZZ高達那裏好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.17,0:10:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,我們也要去凱特爾那兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.18,0:10:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓凱特行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.03,0:10:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱特爾...\n用神殿旁邊的巨大怪東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.07,0:10:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱爾特 在月月人丟棄機器後\n就不在移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.43,0:10:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直被丟再那裏\n成為代表軟弱無力的象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.27,0:10:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是它可以開動\n人們該會注意到過去的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.41,0:11:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還未找到安多拉根亞加瑪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.28,0:11:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,雷達發現類似第一世代\n殖民地的物體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼? 殖民地?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.71,0:11:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找不到其他類似的人工物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.03,0:11:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搜索那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這東西好像放很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.93,0:11:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會動嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.70,0:11:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不動的話還是賣給博物館吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.39,0:11:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.63,0:11:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去看ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.08,0:11:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們真的享分解它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.06,0:11:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.07,0:11:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有辦法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是受教祖之托的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.51,0:12:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉,我要上去駕駛艙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.70,0:12:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們引開看守的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.52,0:12:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我潛入ZZ高達裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.59,0:12:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以輸給比查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.66,0:12:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以動,電池也在可以用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.59,0:12:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰妨礙我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.88,0:12:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可疑的人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.92,0:12:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏!追阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,你在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.91,0:12:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...比查,快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.28,0:12:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.45,0:13:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,ZZ高達...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.98,0:13:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到年代這麼久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.70,0:13:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但一定要開動才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行了\n好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.65,0:13:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要抓到他\n這邊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.69,0:13:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛\n不許動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.44,0:13:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手,捷度,你想要殺人嗎?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.81,0:13:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滾開,比查,不然我真的會刺你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.10,0:13:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,不能再快點嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.48,0:13:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還差一點就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.76,0:13:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,拉莎拉,拉下開關吧\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.62,0:13:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是不動啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別爬上來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.83,0:13:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以讓他們坐上巨神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.40,0:13:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手!別在爬上來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.13,0:13:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會塌下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.22,0:14:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入了,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.42,0:14:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在輪到我了!\n你們小心被踩扁阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.31,0:14:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷..捷度,住手,很危險阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.14,0:14:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快連絡安多拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.76,0:14:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派出加煞C隊抵抗他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨神動了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.20,0:14:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.33,0:14:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,計劃成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.39,0:14:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨神動了,神憤怒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.34,0:14:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.89,0:14:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沖阿,幹掉它們吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.85,0:14:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肅靜!大家冷靜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨神飛上天空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.29,0:14:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想用安多拉的巨神\n打敗飛上天的巨神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.08,0:15:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來...那個少年並不是救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.04,0:15:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜,哥哥現在就去救你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.57,0:15:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滾開!敢妨礙我就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.62,0:15:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關掉艙口,ZZ高達來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.57,0:15:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別阻撓!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.47,0:15:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.80,0:15:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爆炸了,MS甲板受到攻擊\n加煞C爆炸了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.34,0:15:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜...不要緊吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.68,0:15:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的ZZ高達!\n竟然攻擊安多拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.37,0:15:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明大人\n發現安多拉在月月殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.05,0:15:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正受到攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.93,0:15:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\n剛接到無線電話內容了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.46,0:15:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派出龍飛,我要出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.22,0:16:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是巨神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.53,0:16:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨神憤怒了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.22,0:16:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.96,0:16:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉莎大人,在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.84,0:16:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖大人,巨神...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.56,0:16:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快阻止巨神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然月月之地會被摧毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.27,0:16:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不打敗ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.01,0:16:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民地是不會有和平的\n我們是為此而戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.02,0:16:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是巨神是不可以開動的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.89,0:16:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,這次行了,保證能動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.38,0:16:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不動?動阿\n快點動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.45,0:16:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了,動了,拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快到姐姐身邊去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.67,0:17:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此\n不愧是新式MS,很敏捷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.48,0:17:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是安多拉受到攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.72,0:17:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以引來露卡的莉娜\n不會有事吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.67,0:17:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦橋,人質莉娜被關在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.27,0:17:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!在資料室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.81,0:17:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,資料室嗎?好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.70,0:17:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開,我沒空理你們!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.79,0:17:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續壓住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.18,0:17:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要用雷射槍打死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.53,0:18:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱特爾!\n動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.97,0:18:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是..是什麼一回事?神像動了!\n不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.98,0:18:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們阿,不必害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.85,0:18:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱爾特是機器,本來就會動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神像覺醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.90,0:18:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是為了糾正月月人的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不該害怕機器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.39,0:18:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可聽被我驅逐的妹妹說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.07,0:18:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抓住她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教祖大人,請平息巨神之怒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.49,0:18:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅爾!\n戈圖他們在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.19,0:18:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們該負起責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這樣下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.92,0:18:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧,凱爾特會解決問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.68,0:18:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走啊,我們的神像動了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.99,0:18:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁現在回去亞加瑪\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.86,0:19:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,剩下的拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.81,0:19:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.54,0:19:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.55,0:19:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你!把莉娜還給我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手!你想殺死莉娜嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.25,0:19:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要救回莉娜的話,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.04,0:19:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就拿露卡來換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.61,0:19:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿露卡來換?他再說什麼阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.35,0:20:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了,神像贏了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.27,0:20:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱爾特!凱爾特打敗外面的敵人了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.87,0:20:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.25,0:20:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外界有很多類似的機器?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐因為凱爾特沒開動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.70,0:20:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而認定光之教是對的\n這就太武斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說我想利用機器之船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.70,0:20:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對外界宣揚光之教是錯的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.11,0:20:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪那渾蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟然幫助捷度他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.90,0:20:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的! 我另有原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到安卡拉再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.59,0:20:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖先生\n你們躲再哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.41,0:20:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重要的時刻卻躲起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.62,0:20:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.94,0:20:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅爾,為了將宇宙傳到外界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.74,0:20:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把莎拉莎推上教祖之位的人是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.48,0:20:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.79,0:21:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個小殖民地太難生存了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.55,0:21:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我想出去外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.39,0:21:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣有錯嗎?我沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.55,0:21:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓不知情的月月人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.61,0:21:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為宇宙戰爭的犧牲者\n難道就是對的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.55,0:21:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不是自願駕駛MS的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.68,0:21:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為坐上戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.84,0:21:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我妹妹還被敵人抓走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.58,0:21:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽著月月是連地球聯邦軍\n和亞古捷斯都忘記的殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.37,0:21:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在這個情況才是最好的啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.50,0:21:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...被遺忘的感覺太寂寞了\n活的越老越是感傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.32,0:21:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要知足啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.57,0:21:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度,我們走吧\n不是會有新戰艦會再過來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.45,0:21:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.11,0:21:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祝你妹妹平安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.51,0:21:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝,莎拉莎\n外界是很可怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.52,0:21:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.38,0:22:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.75,0:22:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,雖說是井底之蛙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.23,0:22:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但殖民地內的生態循環還算正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.51,0:22:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總比大而不當的殖民地好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.52,0:22:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救回莉娜之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.61,0:22:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們再到那裏玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.27,0:23:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把補給物資搬到亞加瑪的奇怪的大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.07,0:23:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然不小心把戈圖的MS隊帶來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.06,0:23:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖為了完好地得到亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.98,0:24:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我們停靠在拉比安玫瑰的時候進行MS戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.15,0:24:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誒~ 沒完沒了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.75,0:24:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.13,0:24:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪的肉搏戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.30,0:24:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼時候才能見到莉娜？

